@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Xem thực đơn & Lọc món (Filtering)
autonumber

actor "Khách hàng" as Customer
boundary "home.html" as View
control "HomeController" as Controller
participant "CategoryService" as CatService
participant "MenuItemService" as DishService
participant "CategoryRepository" as CatRepo
participant "MenuItemRepository" as DishRepo
database "Database" as DB

' Khách hàng tương tác với bộ lọc
Customer -> View: Chọn Loại món (categoryId) \nhoặc Nhập từ khóa (keyword)
View -> Controller: GET /menu?categoryId=...&keyword=...

activate Controller

' 1. Lấy danh sách danh mục để hiển thị thanh công cụ lọc
Controller -> CatService: getAllCategories()
activate CatService
CatService -> CatRepo: findAll()
activate CatRepo
CatRepo -> DB: SELECT * FROM categories
activate DB
DB --> CatRepo: List<Category>
deactivate DB
CatRepo --> CatService: List<Category>
deactivate CatRepo
CatService --> Controller: List<Category>
deactivate CatService

' 2. Lấy toàn bộ danh sách món ăn
Controller -> DishService: getAllMenuItems()
activate DishService
DishService -> DishRepo: findAll()
activate DishRepo
DishRepo -> DB: SELECT * FROM menu_items
activate DB
DB --> DishRepo: List<MenuItem>
deactivate DB
DishRepo --> DishService: List<MenuItem>
deactivate DishRepo
DishService --> Controller: List<MenuItem>
deactivate DishService

' 3. THỰC HIỆN LỌC (Logic tại Controller)
note over Controller
  **Logic Lọc tại Controller:**
  1. Nếu có categoryId:
     items.filter(i -> i.categoryId == categoryId)
  2. Nếu có keyword:
     items.filter(i -> i.name contains keyword)
end note

' 4. Trả về kết quả
Controller -> Controller: model.addAttribute("menuItems", allitems)
Controller -> Controller: model.addAttribute("currentCategoryId", categoryId)

Controller --> View: Trả về "home.html" (activePage='menu')
deactivate Controller

View --> Customer: Hiển thị danh sách món đã lọc
@enduml